## 6. What is RBAC in Kubernetes?

RBAC (Role-Based Access Control) manages access permissions.

### Components:
- Role – Namespace-level permissions
- ClusterRole – Cluster-wide permissions
- RoleBinding – Binds Role to user/service account
- ClusterRoleBinding – Binds ClusterRole cluster-wide

### Purpose:
- Enforce least privilege
- Secure multi-tenant clusters

