## 7. What is Terraform Workspace?

Terraform Workspace allows managing multiple environments using the same configuration but separate state files.

### Commands:
terraform workspace list
terraform workspace new dev
terraform workspace select dev

### Use Case:
- Separate dev, test, prod without duplicating code

