## 8. If someone manually modifies an EC2 Launch Template, how do you sync it?

This is configuration drift.

### Solution:
If using Terraform:
terraform plan
terraform apply

If using Auto Scaling Group:
- Create new Launch Template version
- Update ASG to latest version
- Perform instance refresh

Best practice: Never allow manual production changes.

